Moët & Chandon Launches 2019 Festive Season in Grand Style With La Vie en Rose Moët & Chandon launched the festive season by hosting the creme de la creme of Lagos society for a night of glitz and glamour with the 2nd instalment of the Secret Location party. This edition was themed La Vie en Rose with Nectar Imperial Rose as the star of the party. <img class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1072065 lazyload" src="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MoetChandon-8595-897x598.jpg" alt="" width="897" height="598" srcset="https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MoetChandon-8595-897x598.jpg 897w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MoetChandon-8595-487x325.jpg 487w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MoetChandon-8595-974x649.jpg 974w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MoetChandon-8595-320x213.jpg 320w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MoetChandon-8595-640x427.jpg 640w,https://guardian.ng/wp-content/uploads/2019/11/MoetChandon-8595-600x400.jpg 600w" sizes="(max-width: 897px) 100vw, 897px" /> It truly was an invitation that could not be turned down, as notable celebrities such as; Omotola Jalade-Ekeinde, Ireti Doyle, Shaffy Bello, Vector, Waje, Abimbola Craig, Beverly Naya, Denola Grey, Deyemi Okanlawon and many more were invited to bask in the luxuries of the day. With delicious rose gold glazed doughnuts from Krispy Kreme, an avant-grand Moët & Chandon Champagne wall – the first of its kind in Lagos, which allowed guests to be served Nectar Imperial Rose from behind a screen. The glamorous decor transformed the secret location – Shiro, into a vision of pink roses and rose gold trimmings. Moet and Chandon La Vie en Rosé, which literally means, “the Life in Pink.” was filled with world-class dining, opulent dress and several grand Moet moments. Guests were treated to the Moet Nectar Imperial Rosé a style distinguished by its bright fruitiness, seductive palate and elegant maturity reflecting the diversity of the House and complementarity of the three grape varietals – the structure of Pinot Noir, the fleshiness of Pinot Meunier and the freshness of Chardonnay. The secret location party, La Vie en Rose, told the world that Moet & Chandon is the only choice when it comes to moments worth celebrating.